pma:database.name: hksv
pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `articles` ( `ArticleID` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `Title` text NOT NULL, `Header` text NOT NULL, `Content` text NOT NULL, `KonselorNIP` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `Timestamp` datetime NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`ArticleID`), KEY `articles_KonselorNIP_foreign` (`KonselorNIP`), CONSTRAINT `articles_KonselorNIP_foreign` FOREIGN KEY (`KonselorNIP`) REFERENCES `dosen` (`NIP`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=30 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb3;
pma:database.pma:view: CREATE ALGORITHM=UNDEFINED DEFINER=`hksvuser`@`localhost` SQL SECURITY DEFINER VIEW `hksv`.`articleviews` AS select `a`.`ArticleID` AS `ArticleID`,`a`.`Title` AS `Title`,`a`.`Header` AS `Header`,`a`.`Content` AS `Content`,`b`.`Nama` AS `KonselorNIP`,`a`.`Timestamp` AS `Timestamp` from (`hksv`.`articles` `a` join `hksv`.`dosen` `b` on((`a`.`KonselorNIP` = `b`.`NIP`)));
pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `beasiswa` ( `idBeasiswa` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `namaBeasiswa` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `donatur` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `nominal` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `syaratSemester` varchar(10) NOT NULL, `syaratIPK` float NOT NULL, `tglDibuka` date NOT NULL, `tglDitutup` date NOT NULL, `status` tinyint(1) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`idBeasiswa`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=9 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb3;

CREATE TABLE `chats` ( `ThreadID` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `ThreadKey` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `MahasiswaNIM` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `KonselorNIP` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `ThreadStatus` enum('OPEN','CLOSED') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'OPEN', `Started_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL, `Closed_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`ThreadID`), KEY `chats_KonselorNIP_foreign` (`KonselorNIP`), CONSTRAINT `chats_KonselorNIP_foreign` FOREIGN KEY (`KonselorNIP`) REFERENCES `dosen` (`NIP`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=44 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb3;

CREATE TABLE `dosen` ( `NIP` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `Nama` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `Prodi` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `Pns` tinyint(1) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`NIP`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb3;

CREATE TABLE `emails` ( `username` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `accountid` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `email` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `notify` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1', PRIMARY KEY (`username`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci;

CREATE TABLE `events` ( `EventID` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `Title` text NOT NULL, `Location` text NOT NULL, `KonselorNIP` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `Timestamp` datetime NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`EventID`), KEY `events_KonselorNIP_foreign` (`KonselorNIP`), CONSTRAINT `events_KonselorNIP_foreign` FOREIGN KEY (`KonselorNIP`) REFERENCES `dosen` (`NIP`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb3;

CREATE TABLE `logs` ( `LogID` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `ActorUsername` text NOT NULL, `Action` text NOT NULL, `Timestamp` datetime NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`LogID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb3;

CREATE TABLE `messages` ( `MessageID` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `SenderID` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `MessageType` enum('text','image','audio') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'text', `Message` text NOT NULL, `ThreadKey` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `Timestamp` datetime NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`MessageID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=171 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb3;

CREATE TABLE `migrations` ( `id` bigint unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `version` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `class` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `group` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `namespace` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `time` int NOT NULL, `batch` int unsigned NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=32 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb3;

CREATE TABLE `notifications` ( `notification_id` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `recipient` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `message` text NOT NULL, `sent` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', PRIMARY KEY (`notification_id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci;

CREATE TABLE `pengajuan` ( `idPengajuan` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `nama` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `nim` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `prodi` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `semester` int NOT NULL, `ip1` float NOT NULL, `ip2` float NOT NULL, `ip3` float NOT NULL, `ip4` float NOT NULL, `ip5` float NOT NULL, `ip6` float NOT NULL, `ipk` float NOT NULL, `namaBeasiswa` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `tanggalPengajuan` date NOT NULL, `status` enum('Diproses','Disetujui','Ditolak') CHARACTER SET utf8mb3 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NOT NULL DEFAULT 'Diproses', `cv` text, `pic` text CHARACTER SET utf8mb3 COLLATE utf8_general_ci, `nip` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`idPengajuan`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=26 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb3;
pma:database.pma:view: CREATE ALGORITHM=UNDEFINED DEFINER=`hksvuser`@`localhost` SQL SECURITY DEFINER VIEW `hksv`.`pengajuankonseling` AS select `hksv`.`request`.`RequestID` AS `RequestID`,`hksv`.`request`.`MahasiswaNIM` AS `MahasiswaNIM`,`hksv`.`request`.`MahasiswaPS` AS `MahasiswaPS`,`hksv`.`request`.`MahasiswaNama` AS `MahasiswaNama`,`hksv`.`request`.`RequestDetail` AS `RequestDetail`,`hksv`.`request`.`ThreadKey` AS `ThreadKey`,`hksv`.`request`.`Timestamp` AS `Timestamp` from `hksv`.`request` where (`hksv`.`request`.`ThreadKey` = '');
pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `penilaian` ( `idPenilaian` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `idPengajuan` int NOT NULL, `kemampuanAkademik` int NOT NULL, `kemampuanLisan` int NOT NULL, `kemampuanTertulis` int NOT NULL, `motivasi` int NOT NULL, `kestabilan` int NOT NULL, `kreativitas` int NOT NULL, `kemampuanBerkelompok` int NOT NULL, `kemampuanTeknis` int NOT NULL, `catatan` text NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`idPenilaian`), UNIQUE KEY `idPengajuan` (`idPengajuan`), CONSTRAINT `penilaian_idPengajuan_foreign` FOREIGN KEY (`idPengajuan`) REFERENCES `pengajuan` (`idPengajuan`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=16 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb3;

CREATE TABLE `request` ( `RequestID` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `MahasiswaNIM` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `MahasiswaPS` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8mb3 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NOT NULL, `MahasiswaNama` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `RequestDetail` text NOT NULL, `ThreadKey` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `Timestamp` datetime NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`RequestID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=34 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb3;

CREATE TABLE `role` ( `Id` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `NIP` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `Role` enum('dosen','konselor','sekprodi','admin') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'dosen', PRIMARY KEY (`Id`), KEY `role_NIP_foreign` (`NIP`), CONSTRAINT `role_NIP_foreign` FOREIGN KEY (`NIP`) REFERENCES `dosen` (`NIP`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=162 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb3;

Kesadaran akan pentingnya kesehatan jiwa belakangan ini menjadi isu yang ramai diperbincangkan di masyarakat, namun masih ternyata masih banyak stigma negatif yang menyelimutinya juga. Selain dianggap aib, masalah biaya pula yang menyebabkan para penderita gangguan kejiwaan tidak tersentuh oleh oleh penanganan profesional. Jadi apakah hanya orang kaya yang boleh sakit jiwa?
